      "rationale": "Validation performed on the exact non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design subject to the COU, under the identical ASTM F1717 protocol specified in the intended use. Testing conducted across two independent laboratories (Laboratory A, n=6; Laboratory B, n=5) to assess inter-laboratory reproducibility. High relevance to COU confirmed."
