    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single-condition testing; this gap is accepted given the direct bench-test comparison provides high confidence in model predictions for the specific ASTM F1717 configuration. Quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across N=11 constructs from two laboratories. Model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission decision.",
